description: BLACKSBURG, VA --Cayla King hit a dagger 3-pointer with 1:10 left in the fourth quarter to put Virginia Tech up 70-61, and the Hokies secured a 73-63 victory over the Georgia Tech Yellow Jackets at home Thursday.
